{"tid":2263410,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"啟示書院(指南針學院), 改名做「現代持續教育」?","createTime":"2020-10-30T01:12:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-01T12:53:51.000Z","uid":204929,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"593b667fe564d4065b283e89a94d370d0c36fb56","tid":2263410,"uid":204929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T01:12:34.000Z","msg":"唔知係咪<span class=\"red\">又想呃入世未深人</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?<br />\n學歷<span class=\"red\">冇認受性</span>?<br />\n唔知會唔<span class=\"red\">會呃鳩人, 再報讀冇用嘅課程?</span><br />\n<br />\n雖然唔知點解, 不過大家最好都係打電話去香港教育局問清楚, 因為呢啲先至係正式嘅資料證明學歷!院校自己話香港承認係冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />!<br />\n<br />\n佢唔知遲啲會唔<span class=\"red\">會用黑社會手段打壓人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?唔知會唔會又想剷人新聞, 侵害新聞自由</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nP.S.我只係問清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 冇抹黑!<br />\n唔好一陣間又喺度誹謗一眾嘅連登仔!"},{"pid":"bbfe9baf3d63f60dbcb6b792a9a91da843af64a8","tid":2263410,"uid":204929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T01:20:40.000Z","msg":"環球專上書院係呃人，同傳銷無分別<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fzyAxT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fzyAxT</a><br />\n#7 回覆 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n或者都可以參考下相關資料判斷下"},{"pid":"73140193a28bbdbe6c1e0cb0405824925d283a19","tid":2263410,"uid":204929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T10:08:39.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6a3fd3a771fb08f236ad8a4ac1ac1204738e3754","tid":2263410,"uid":204929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T14:58:14.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5e63ee2ddc9b4058c5a076f386af7438f7ee3dc4","tid":2263410,"uid":204929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T16:31:28.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e3aa5fff2a77dc828e9a8639189e5b97da58dd7a","tid":2263410,"uid":204929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30